        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>FreelancerHub's mission is, and always will be, &ldquo;Customers First&rdquo;. We understand, acknowledge and respect any individual's right to privacy and the concerns one may have in regard to privacy and security. We recognize the importance of protecting the privacy of information provided by our customers, as well as, general users of our website.</p>
